<p> </p>

<p><strong>Warehouse for sale: An evergreen real estate investment</strong></p>

<p>A warehouse is a spacious building used to store goods such as raw materials and manufactured goods before being exported or distributed to physical stores, resellers, or other clients. It is also where large construction vehicles are often parked and stored for safety purposes.</p>

<p>In the advent of the pandemic, the demand for warehouses just got stronger since retail business has shifted online, increasing the demand for warehouse spaces to store goods that were stored in physical stores before. Even though everything can go back to the old normal, it is safe to conclude that online selling and shopping are here to stay due to their convenience. As a result, it is safe to say that warehouses are an evergreen investment.</p>

<p> </p>

<p><strong>Locations where you can buy warehouses for sale</strong></p>

<p>You can find warehouses in almost all parts of the Philippines, especially in industrial sites located in and outside the Metro. In the National Capital Region, you can find <strong>warehouses for sale</strong> in <a data-mce-href="https://www.lamudi.com.ph/metro-manila/quezon-city/commercial/warehouse/buy/" href="https://www.lamudi.com.ph/metro-manila/quezon-city/commercial/warehouse/buy/">Quezon City</a>, <a data-mce-href="https://www.lamudi.com.ph/metro-manila/makati/commercial/warehouse/buy/" href="https://www.lamudi.com.ph/metro-manila/makati/commercial/warehouse/buy/">Makati</a>, <a data-mce-href="https://www.lamudi.com.ph/metro-manila/taguig/commercial/warehouse/buy/" href="https://www.lamudi.com.ph/metro-manila/taguig/commercial/warehouse/buy/">Taguig</a>, <a data-mce-href="https://www.lamudi.com.ph/metro-manila/manila/commercial/warehouse/buy/" href="https://www.lamudi.com.ph/metro-manila/manila/commercial/warehouse/buy/">Manila</a>, <a data-mce-href="https://www.lamudi.com.ph/metro-manila/mandaluyong/commercial/warehouse/buy/" href="https://www.lamudi.com.ph/metro-manila/mandaluyong/commercial/warehouse/buy/">Mandaluyong</a>, <a data-mce-href="https://www.lamudi.com.ph/metro-manila/muntinlupa/commercial/warehouse/buy/" href="https://www.lamudi.com.ph/metro-manila/muntinlupa/commercial/warehouse/buy/">Muntinlupa</a>, <a data-mce-href="https://www.lamudi.com.ph/metro-manila/san-juan-5/commercial/warehouse/buy/" href="https://www.lamudi.com.ph/metro-manila/san-juan-5/commercial/warehouse/buy/">San Juan</a>, <a data-mce-href="https://www.lamudi.com.ph/metro-manila/paranaque/commercial/warehouse/buy/" href="https://www.lamudi.com.ph/metro-manila/paranaque/commercial/warehouse/buy/">Parañaque</a>, <a data-mce-href="https://www.lamudi.com.ph/metro-manila/las-pinas/commercial/warehouse/buy/" href="https://www.lamudi.com.ph/metro-manila/las-pinas/commercial/warehouse/buy/">Las Piñas</a>, and <a data-mce-href="https://www.lamudi.com.ph/metro-manila/pasig/commercial/warehouse/buy/" href="https://www.lamudi.com.ph/metro-manila/pasig/commercial/warehouse/buy/">Pasig</a>. These warehouses are located either in the commercial districts or quiet residential neighborhoods of these cities.</p>

<p>Outside the Metro, you can find warehouses in industrial parks and zones located in <a data-mce-href="https://www.lamudi.com.ph/cebu/commercial/warehouse/buy/" href="https://www.lamudi.com.ph/cebu/commercial/warehouse/buy/">Cebu</a>, <a data-mce-href="https://www.lamudi.com.ph/cavite/commercial/warehouse/buy/" href="https://www.lamudi.com.ph/cavite/commercial/warehouse/buy/">Cavite</a>, <a data-mce-href="https://www.lamudi.com.ph/laguna/commercial/warehouse/buy/" href="https://www.lamudi.com.ph/laguna/commercial/warehouse/buy/">Laguna</a>, <a data-mce-href="https://www.lamudi.com.ph/rizal/commercial/warehouse/buy/" href="https://www.lamudi.com.ph/rizal/commercial/warehouse/buy/">Rizal</a>, <a data-mce-href="https://www.lamudi.com.ph/davao-del-sur/commercial/warehouse/buy/" href="https://www.lamudi.com.ph/davao-del-sur/commercial/warehouse/buy/">Davao del Sur</a>, <a data-mce-href="https://www.lamudi.com.ph/pampanga/commercial/warehouse/buy/" href="https://www.lamudi.com.ph/pampanga/commercial/warehouse/buy/">Pampanga</a>, <a data-mce-href="https://www.lamudi.com.ph/batangas/commercial/warehouse/buy/" href="https://www.lamudi.com.ph/batangas/commercial/warehouse/buy/">Batangas</a>, <a data-mce-href="https://www.lamudi.com.ph/bulacan/commercial/warehouse/buy/" href="https://www.lamudi.com.ph/bulacan/commercial/warehouse/buy/">Bulacan</a>, and <a data-mce-href="https://www.lamudi.com.ph/benguet/commercial/warehouse/buy/" href="https://www.lamudi.com.ph/benguet/commercial/warehouse/buy/">Benguet</a>. So wherever you or your business is located, you can find a perfectly sized warehouse that suits your business' needs.</p>

<p> </p>

<p><strong>The price tag of a warehouse</strong></p>

<p>Warehouses in Metro Manila measure 9 to 10,942 square meters. Some have multiple floors while others are just one-storey high. These warehouses cost anywhere between PhP 762,000 to PhP 1,700,000,000. Outside the metro, <strong>warehouses for sale</strong> cost PhP 2,320,000 to PhP 199,500,000.</p>

<p> </p>

<p><strong>Why a warehouse is a worthwhile investment</strong></p>

<p>Warehouses are often used for heavy industry businesses such as manufacturing, automotive, and construction. If your business is related to these fields, it is ideal to purchase a warehouse to make sure your products and equipment are safe and accessible.</p>

<p>Owning a warehouse located in an industrial park is also ideal because you get to position your business close to other businesses, making yourself visible to clients visiting the industrial park.</p>

<p>Sta. Rosa in Laguna and Clark Freeport Zone in Pampanga are places close to the Metro where industrial parks and economic activities are booming, so it is best to seek <strong>warehouses for sale</strong> in these areas if you reside in the Metro or on its outskirts. Bacolod City, Cebu, and Davao are locations outside Luzon where it is best to invest in a warehouse. These urbanized provinces in Visayas and Mindanao are the center of trading and commerce, making them ideal places for starting a business.  </p>

<p> </p>

<p><strong>Investment and business opportunities</strong></p>

<p>As mentioned at the outset, warehouses are an in-demand real estate property. Even though you might not have a business that needs a warehouse, you can earn from your property by leasing it to entrepreneurs and business owners who need a warehouse for their business.</p>

<p> </p>

<p><strong>FAQs</strong></p>

<p><strong>Are there </strong><a data-mce-href="https://www.lamudi.com.ph/commercial/warehouse/buy/price:2500000-5000000/" href="https://www.lamudi.com.ph/commercial/warehouse/buy/price:2500000-5000000/"><strong>warehouses that cost PhP 2.5M to PhP 5M</strong></a><strong>?</strong></p>

<p>Yes. In this price range, you can find 40 to 650 square meter warehouses located in Bacoor, Manila, and Bacnotan.</p>

<p><strong>Are there </strong><a data-mce-href="https://www.lamudi.com.ph/commercial/warehouse/buy/price:7500000-10000000/" href="https://www.lamudi.com.ph/commercial/warehouse/buy/price:7500000-10000000/"><strong>warehouses for sale below PhP 10M</strong></a><strong>?</strong></p>

<p>Yes. The sizes of warehouses that have this price tag range from 251 to 1500 square meters.</p>

<p><strong>What type of </strong><a data-mce-href="https://www.lamudi.com.ph/commercial/warehouse/buy/price:20000000-30000000/" href="https://www.lamudi.com.ph/commercial/warehouse/buy/price:20000000-30000000/"><strong>warehouse can I buy for a budget of PhP 20M to PhP 30M</strong></a><strong>?</strong></p>

<p>You can purchase a 400 square meter warehouse in Las Piñas for PhP 22,000,000. Add PhP 5,000,000 to that, and you can purchase a 520 square meter warehouse in Santa Cruz, Manila. If you have PhP 30,000,000, you can purchase a three-storey warehouse in Sucat with a floor area of 700 square meters.</p>
